title: Yaman Kattalai
overview: Guru Commits Suicide Because Guru Steals the Jewels of Kamali, Who is About to Get Married, and Tries to Commit Suicide Because She is in This Situation Because of Him. In Emalok Yaman Asks Him to Give Him Life Again and Ask Him to Marry Kamali and Eventually Guru Himself Marries Kamali.
